law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 274, sec. 165, effective July 1, 1972. -- Amended 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 263, sec. 2, effective June 18, 1970. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 1, effective March 24, 1952. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 1. effective July 1, 1946.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Shares, classes and series of--Provisions for voting powers, special rights, restrictions, redemption, dividends, and priority on dissolution--Conversion or exchange--Provisions concerning division of classes into series.
